survey_response.review_text: Our experience with Dr. Kashif Syed is simply amazing. No doubt, he is a wonderful doctor. The good thing about the doctor is that he just doesn't treat the problem from its roots but also suggests us in a way that these sort of issues doesn't arise again in future. He kept us on minimal medication and gave suggestions to improve our lifestyle and how small changes can make a big difference in our lives. We would personally recommend him. Very down to earth, empathetic and caring nature.   Thank you sir for giving us the right treatment!

Dr. Kashif is a godsend. He’s a very patient person who genuinely cares about his patients. He relates well to people and takes time to listen and takes appropriate action on the symptoms. 

He’s the best ever! Never rushed, always willing to listen and so smart. I can’t imagine going to anyone else. 

He is good at building trust with his patients. HIGHLY Grateful for his experience & wide range of knowledge. I would recommend Dr. Kashif to anyone seeking a kind, compassionate, and brilliant doctor. His staff is amazing!

Dr. Kashif taught me an extremely important lesson in medical care - to approach an illness holistically and not be anxious about it. My anxiety had caused my BP to spike and manifested other scary physical symptoms. He gave me a very patient hearing and explained in great detail about how anxiety affects physical health. He gave me a plan of action and reassured me every time I made progress. He truly is a fantastic physician who looks at not just the illness but also the person and is focused on long term wellness rather than just pushing pills your way. I am extremely grateful to be in his care!
